248
00:16:02,503 --> 00:16:04,172
Don't be silly. Get your hand off me.

249
00:16:05,882 --> 00:16:06,924
It's okay.

250
00:16:07,925 --> 00:16:09,510
Who would help you if not me?

251
00:16:10,511 --> 00:16:12,263
