253
00:16:15,766 --> 00:16:16,934
My nose!

254
00:16:17,018 --> 00:16:18,269
I'll ask him myself.

255
00:16:19,228 --> 00:16:20,688
Hey, Seon. Listen...

256
00:16:20,771 --> 00:16:22,106
Listen to me first, Seon!

257
00:16:25,651 --> 00:16:27,570
You need to prepare for divorce now

258
00:16:27,653 --> 00:16:29,322
to get the most you can!

259
00:16:31,657 --> 00:16:33,618
My offer to work together.

260
00:16:33,701 --> 00:16:35,661
It's still valid,
so think it through carefully.

261
00:16:38,164 --> 00:16:39,582
SEON

262
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:42,585
- Hey, Seon.
- Hello?

263
00:16:43,794 --> 00:16:45,963
- Who are you with right now?
- Hang on.

264
00:16:46,839 --> 00:16:48,591
Can you come to where I am?

265
00:16:49,050 --> 00:16:50,468
Let's talk in person.

266
00:16:51,177 --> 00:16:52,303
Where are you?

267
00:16:53,429 --> 00:16:54,931
I'm at Hee-ju's realtor's office.

268
00:16:55,348 --> 00:16:56,474
Okay, wait there.

269
00:16:57,391 --> 00:16:58,392
Okay.

270
00:17:08,277 --> 00:17:11,614
M&amp;A REALTORS

271
00:17:14,951 --> 00:17:15,952
Su-jong.

272
00:17:24,168 --> 00:17:25,169
She's dead.

273
00:17:27,213 --> 00:17:28,214
Did you kill her?

274
00:17:28,297 --> 00:17:29,382
I'm not crazy.

275
00:17:36,514 --> 00:17:37,515
INCOMING CALL

276
00:17:47,275 --> 00:17:48,693
Darn it.

277
00:17:54,073 --> 00:17:56,492
She was dead when I woke up.

278
00:17:56,867 --> 00:17:59,203
I really didn't do anything.

279
00:18:01,539 --> 00:18:02,540
Hang on.

280
00:18:02,999 --> 00:18:04,250
What was "divide the assets" about?

281
00:18:04,959 --> 00:18:07,044
Did you tell Hee-ju
you wanted a divorce?

282
00:18:07,753 --> 00:18:09,046
How do you know about that?

283
00:18:09,714 --> 00:18:11,132
Hwal-sung told me.

284
00:18:12,592 --> 00:18:14,010
How did he know?

285
00:18:14,093 --> 00:18:16,721
He played a recording of your voice.

286
00:18:22,101 --> 00:18:23,102
Where's my share?

287
00:18:24,478 --> 00:18:26,439
Your share? What's that?

288
00:18:27,189 --> 00:18:28,816
We agreed to split it.

289
00:18:28,899 --> 00:18:31,319
That went out the window
the moment you called the police.

290
00:18:31,402 --> 00:18:32,528
I explained.

291
00:18:32,612 --> 00:18:34,780
I didn't call them.
My mother-in-law did.

292
00:18:34,864 --> 00:18:36,574
You're talking your way out again.

293
00:18:37,617 --> 00:18:39,035
Hwal-sung did this.

294
00:18:39,535 --> 00:18:40,536
Did what?

295
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,163
Well...

296
00:18:42,246 --> 00:18:43,748
Not long ago

297
00:18:44,332 --> 00:18:46,751
he came to me and asked
for his share of my property.

298
00:18:46,834 --> 00:18:49,754
He kicked up a fuss,
and I turned him down.

299
00:18:50,504 --> 00:18:53,257
He plans to create a rift between us

300
00:18:53,341 --> 00:18:56,469
to take Se-yoon Building from me.

301
00:18:58,054 --> 00:18:59,388
But that...

302
00:18:59,889 --> 00:19:02,058
What does that have to do
with Hee-ju's death?

303
00:19:02,141 --> 00:19:04,977
Would Hee-ju have given him
that recording for free?

304
00:19:05,770 --> 00:19:08,272
She demanded something
in exchange for it

305
00:19:08,356 --> 00:19:10,566
and that blew up into a fight.

306
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:12,443
While I was asleep

307
00:19:12,526 --> 00:19:13,944
they talked about shares
and the recording

308
00:19:14,028 --> 00:19:15,237
and then this happened.

309
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,408
That's just too insane.

310
00:19:19,825 --> 00:19:22,703
Would Hwal-sung
kill someone over that?

311
00:19:22,787 --> 00:19:23,871
Don't you know what he's like?

312
00:19:24,747 --> 00:19:26,582
Don't you remember
he planned the kidnapping?

313
00:19:26,666 --> 00:19:28,501
I'm going to divorce Yi-gyeong.

314
00:19:29,377 --> 00:19:30,795
We'll both get divorced

315
00:19:32,505 --> 00:19:33,798
and take over

316
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,591
the redevelopment project.

317
00:19:36,967 --> 00:19:38,469
With the right plan

318
00:19:39,011 --> 00:19:40,221
we can pull it off.

319
00:19:42,306 --> 00:19:44,642
Once he gets
his share in the business

320
00:19:45,101 --> 00:19:47,520
he'll grab me by the throat
and strangle me.

321
00:19:50,064 --> 00:19:52,149
I wonder where Hee-ju's phone is.

322
00:19:56,821 --> 00:19:57,863
What are you doing?

323
00:19:57,947 --> 00:19:59,115
Her phone.

324
00:19:59,198 --> 00:20:00,991
I want to see the call log.

325
00:20:05,162 --> 00:20:06,163
Come here, Seon.

326
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:08,833
Hello? Is anyone inside?

327
00:20:13,295 --> 00:20:14,505
Darn it.

328
00:20:18,134 --> 00:20:19,135
Hang on.

329
00:20:23,222 --> 00:20:24,932
What's going on?

330
00:20:34,233 --> 00:20:35,234
Is he gone?

331
00:20:36,652 --> 00:20:38,404
- Yes.
- Are you sure?

332
00:20:38,779 --> 00:20:39,864
Yes, he's gone.

333
00:20:42,658 --> 00:20:43,659
Seon.

334
00:20:46,370 --> 00:20:47,371
Do you trust me?

335
00:20:49,957 --> 00:20:50,958
What?

336
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:52,501
You don't trust me?

337
00:20:54,879 --> 00:20:56,213
When you're drunk

338
00:20:57,131 --> 00:20:59,341
- you do sleep through anything.
- Right.

339
00:21:00,259 --> 00:21:01,469
I swear.

340
00:21:03,012 --> 00:21:05,222
I have no memory of anything
after I fell asleep.

341
00:21:18,694 --> 00:21:19,862
Why? What is it?

342
00:21:19,945 --> 00:21:21,238
Ms. Kim.

343
00:21:21,322 --> 00:21:22,323
Where are you?

344
00:21:22,406 --> 00:21:24,283
We're celebrating
Da-rae getting into Harvard.

345
00:21:24,366 --> 00:21:25,493
You're coming, right?

346
00:21:25,576 --> 00:21:27,495
- S-jong, she got in.
- What?

347
00:21:27,578 --> 00:21:28,579
Da-rae got in.

348
00:21:28,662 --> 00:21:30,414
- She did?
- Hang on.

349
00:21:31,999 --> 00:21:33,125
DA-RAE'S ACADEMY TEACHER

350
00:21:33,209 --> 00:21:35,628
Da-rae got in?
Did you hear from them?

351
00:21:36,462 --> 00:21:37,588
You didn't know?

352
00:21:38,255 --> 00:21:40,007
She received
the acceptance e-mail last night.

353
00:21:40,424 --> 00:21:42,176
I'll forward you
the one they sent us.

354
00:21:42,676 --> 00:21:43,677
Her letter of acceptance.

355
00:21:46,555 --> 00:21:48,307
Da-rae did it.

356
00:21:49,266 --> 00:21:51,018
This is incredible.

357
00:21:51,519 --> 00:21:52,520
Hang on.

358
00:21:53,395 --> 00:21:54,772
If they sent the e-mail last night

359
00:21:54,855 --> 00:21:56,398
why didn't Da-rae say anything?

360
00:21:56,649 --> 00:21:58,692
She didn't say? Was she busy?

361
00:21:59,485 --> 00:22:02,905
No, she was in her room all night.

362
00:22:04,782 --> 00:22:06,325
Make a video call.

363
00:22:08,661 --> 00:22:16,085
MY LOVING DAUGHTER

364
00:22:16,585 --> 00:22:18,337
- Why won't she pick up?
- She won't answer.

365
00:22:23,259 --> 00:22:24,510
There's no response.

366
00:22:24,593 --> 00:22:25,803
Darn it.

367
00:22:36,146 --> 00:22:37,731
I WANT TO BE ALONE

368
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:42,611
Congratulations on getting in, kids.

369
00:22:42,695 --> 00:22:45,197
I knew you'd make it.

370
00:22:45,489 --> 00:22:46,532
Applause.

371
00:22:47,408 --> 00:22:48,409
Congratulations.

372
00:22:48,492 --> 00:22:49,827
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

373
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:53,372
Congratulations on getting in.

374
00:22:53,455 --> 00:22:58,669
I knew you'd get it done, Da-rae.

375
00:23:00,588 --> 00:23:03,090
Da-rae, Jeong-min, Bo-mi.
Blow out the candles.

376
00:23:03,173 --> 00:23:04,174
Get ready.

377
00:23:04,258 --> 00:23:06,260
WE HAVE BRAGGING RIGHTS FOREVER!
WE'RE GOING TO THE IVY LEAGUE!

378
00:23:06,343 --> 00:23:07,344
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

379
00:23:07,428 --> 00:23:09,054
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

380
00:23:09,138 --> 00:23:10,472
Congratulations!

381
00:23:10,723 --> 00:23:12,391
- I'm dead jealous.
- Seriously.

382
00:23:12,641 --> 00:23:13,642
- Congratulations.
- Seriously.

383
00:23:13,726 --> 00:23:14,977
- Congratulations.
- Good for you.

384
00:23:15,603 --> 00:23:17,730
Da-rae, why aren't you picking up?

385
00:23:18,647 --> 00:23:20,065
Do you want soda?

386
00:23:20,149 --> 00:23:21,317
- I'll have some.
- What about you?

387
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,401
Are you all right?

388
00:23:23,652 --> 00:23:25,613
- I've been waiting to dig in.
- Give me some, too.

389
00:23:25,696 --> 00:23:26,780
Okay, hang on.

390
00:23:35,748 --> 00:23:38,292
YOU KILLED ME

391
00:23:42,087 --> 00:23:45,633
MY MOTHER-IN-LAW, AND THE CAFÉ OWNER

392
00:23:54,058 --> 00:23:55,351
What are you thinking about?

393
00:24:03,192 --> 00:24:04,526
JUST... ABOUT THE TUITION?

394
00:24:04,610 --> 00:24:06,278
Your father owns a building.

395
00:24:06,570 --> 00:24:07,696
Why would you worry?

396
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:13,118
The others ordered some food.

397
00:24:13,202 --> 00:24:14,286
Do you want to join them?

398
00:24:15,329 --> 00:24:16,330
Let's go.

399
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,216
It's a shame she's dead,
but it can't be helped.

400
00:24:27,716 --> 00:24:28,717
Right.

401
00:24:30,427 --> 00:24:31,637
What can't be helped?

402
00:24:34,014 --> 00:24:35,182
Let's clean it up.

403
00:24:37,351 --> 00:24:39,520
M&amp;A REALTORS

404
00:24:39,603 --> 00:24:41,897
All the cameras in the neighborhood

405
00:24:42,272 --> 00:24:44,608
will have filmed you
coming in here with her.

406
00:24:47,987 --> 00:24:51,615
M&amp;A REALTORS

407
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:53,951
That's right.

408
00:24:54,702 --> 00:24:56,161
We drank, I passed out

409
00:24:56,245 --> 00:24:58,580
and she was dead when I woke up.

410
00:25:00,124 --> 00:25:02,126
I was recently a kidnapping suspect

411
00:25:02,584 --> 00:25:04,336
and was even interrogated about it.

412
00:25:05,087 --> 00:25:07,047
I can't think of a way out.

413
00:25:07,548 --> 00:25:08,924
You said you thought
Hwal-sung did it.

414
00:25:10,467 --> 00:25:12,678
Won't his arrest solve everything?

415
00:25:13,470 --> 00:25:16,640
At least we'll get to find out
what happened during the night.

416
00:25:16,932 --> 00:25:19,351
We must identify the murderer.

417
00:25:20,227 --> 00:25:23,063
Or at least find proof
that it wasn't you.

418
00:25:24,690 --> 00:25:26,984
It would be best for Hee-ju
if we were to find out

419
00:25:27,901 --> 00:25:29,403
who did this to her.

420
00:25:39,913 --> 00:25:40,914
Seon.

421
00:25:42,583 --> 00:25:44,001
Thank you for trusting me.

422
00:25:45,419 --> 00:25:47,713
We'll talk again
after we sort this out.

423
00:25:48,714 --> 00:25:50,257
We need Da-rae to go to Harvard.

424
00:25:51,008 --> 00:25:52,009
Right.

425
00:25:54,219 --> 00:25:55,304
So...

426
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:58,599
We have a place to hide her.

427
00:25:59,099 --> 00:26:00,768
The problem is, how do we move her?

428
00:26:13,947 --> 00:26:14,948
What are you doing?

429
00:26:16,075 --> 00:26:17,284
Strip her, Su-jong.

430
00:26:17,367 --> 00:26:18,368
What?

431
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:20,079
Take her clothes off.

432
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,463
- Her car key.
- Yes.

433
00:26:29,755 --> 00:26:30,756
Okay.

434
00:27:31,108 --> 00:27:32,776
- Su-jong, let's go.
- Okay.

435
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:36,280
I can't find her phone.
Someone must've taken it.

436
00:27:36,363 --> 00:27:37,364
Let's go for now.

437
00:28:17,863 --> 00:28:19,364
Is this the right way?

438
00:28:20,699 --> 00:28:22,117
We must go home first.

439
00:28:23,410 --> 00:28:25,078
We need to be seen
on our neighborhood cameras.

440
00:28:26,496 --> 00:28:29,082
You two get out first,
then meet me at the back.

441
00:28:30,334 --> 00:28:31,543
Okay.

442
00:29:20,092 --> 00:29:21,093
Careful.

443
00:29:35,607 --> 00:29:36,608
I'll get down first.

444
00:29:45,033 --> 00:29:46,285
She's so heavy.

445
00:29:50,038 --> 00:29:51,164
Get in.

446
00:30:00,632 --> 00:30:01,633
Let's go.

447
00:30:14,813 --> 00:30:18,233
PROVIDE A MEASURE!

448
00:30:18,317 --> 00:30:21,737
DO NOT DRIVE US OUT!

449
00:30:43,216 --> 00:30:44,718
See if anyone is coming.

450
00:30:45,969 --> 00:30:47,304
- No one's around.
- Wait.

451
00:30:47,721 --> 00:30:48,722
Hold on.

452
00:30:53,477 --> 00:30:54,853
Wait, what do we do now?

453
00:30:54,936 --> 00:30:55,937
One second.

454
00:30:56,646 --> 00:30:58,398
- Let's get her closer.
- Closer?

455
00:30:58,482 --> 00:30:59,733
- Just a little more.
- Okay.

456
00:30:59,816 --> 00:31:00,984
Get her closer.

457
00:31:01,985 --> 00:31:03,070
Closer.

458
00:31:03,153 --> 00:31:04,654
Get her closer.

459
00:31:05,113 --> 00:31:06,156
Closer.

460
00:31:06,490 --> 00:31:07,574
Can you lift her?

461
00:31:09,868 --> 00:31:11,078
Are we allowed to do this?

462
00:31:12,037 --> 00:31:13,038
Let's see.

463
00:31:25,675 --> 00:31:26,676
Su-jong.

464
00:31:27,427 --> 00:31:29,262
- Let me get changed first.
- Okay.

465
00:31:30,472 --> 00:31:34,476
KEEP OUT

466
00:31:47,280 --> 00:31:48,323
Handcuffs.

467
00:31:48,698 --> 00:31:49,699
Prison uniform.

468
00:31:50,534 --> 00:31:51,535
Handcuffs?

469
00:31:51,618 --> 00:31:54,079
If you don't do anything,
your husband will go to prison.

470
00:31:55,414 --> 00:31:56,665
Keep this on you.

471
00:31:56,748 --> 00:31:58,667
Good things will happen to your child

472
00:31:59,084 --> 00:32:00,836
and your husband will be fine.

473
00:32:21,148 --> 00:32:22,149
Are we done?

474
00:32:22,649 --> 00:32:23,650
Yes.

475
00:32:25,569 --> 00:32:26,695
I have no idea

476
00:32:26,945 --> 00:32:28,780
what I'm doing right now.

477
00:32:29,156 --> 00:32:31,283
I'm sorry.
I'll make sure I catch the culprit.

478
00:32:33,034 --> 00:32:34,286
I'll report you

479
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:36,538
if you don't.

480
00:32:36,788 --> 00:32:39,124
Yes, pin this on me.

481
00:32:39,416 --> 00:32:41,084
I won't tell them that you helped.

482
00:32:42,586 --> 00:32:44,004
What do you mean?

483
00:32:44,296 --> 00:32:45,922
How am I your accomplice?

484
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:48,675
I didn't say you were.

485
00:32:50,802 --> 00:32:52,471
Forget it. Good grief.

486
00:33:00,645 --> 00:33:01,897
MY LOVING DAUGHTER

487
00:33:04,065 --> 00:33:05,484
Su-jong, look.

488
00:33:05,567 --> 00:33:07,068
I got a message from Da-rae.

489
00:33:07,569 --> 00:33:10,697
MOM, I KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
BETWEEN YOU AND YI-GYEONG

490
00:33:11,281 --> 00:33:12,282
What is this?

491
00:33:14,075 --> 00:33:15,577
Wait, how did she know?

492
00:33:17,537 --> 00:33:18,663
I have no idea.

493
00:33:19,414 --> 00:33:20,540
What?

494
00:33:20,624 --> 00:33:23,084
She won't reply to my message
or pick up her phone.

495
00:33:24,503 --> 00:33:27,339
- I need to go and see her right now.
- Yes, Seon.

496
00:33:27,422 --> 00:33:29,508
Grab a cab.
I have to get rid of the car.

497
00:33:29,591 --> 00:33:31,426
- You should go.
- Yes, okay.

498
00:33:34,471 --> 00:33:35,972
Hello, Da-rae's teacher?

499
00:33:36,056 --> 00:33:38,683
I just saw the text message.

500
00:33:40,227 --> 00:33:41,853
Where should I go?

501
00:33:47,067 --> 00:33:48,860
Darn it.

502
00:33:50,946 --> 00:33:52,572
- Eat some chicken.
- I want the drumstick.

503
00:33:53,323 --> 00:33:54,991
- Here it is.
- That's so unfair.

504
00:33:55,867 --> 00:33:57,994
What do you mean you know everything?

505
00:33:58,828 --> 00:34:00,330
- What do you want?
- Soda.

506
00:34:00,413 --> 00:34:01,414
Soda?

507
00:34:01,498 --> 00:34:02,541
I KNOW...

508
00:34:02,624 --> 00:34:04,334
- He's taking the first sip.
- It doesn't matter.

509
00:34:04,709 --> 00:34:05,710
Unbelievable.

510
00:34:05,794 --> 00:34:09,089
I KNOW WHAT YOU AND DAD DID

511
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:11,883
You need to share.

512
00:34:12,634 --> 00:34:15,720
INCOMING VIDEO CALL
MOM

513
00:34:17,347 --> 00:34:18,557
- Stop it.
- What?

514
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:19,724
Cut it out!

515
00:34:30,277 --> 00:34:32,112
- Soda, please.
- Did you eat this again?

516
00:34:32,195 --> 00:34:33,363
How many pieces did you eat?

517
00:34:33,822 --> 00:34:34,906
- Three.
- Three?

518
00:34:40,036 --> 00:34:41,413
Please take one.

519
00:34:41,496 --> 00:34:42,706
ANTI-DEVELOPMENT COMMITTEE

520
00:34:42,789 --> 00:34:44,291
- Thank you.
- Sure.

521
00:34:44,374 --> 00:34:47,002
UNITE AND FIGHT

522
00:34:47,085 --> 00:34:48,336
Please put one on your head.

523
00:34:48,587 --> 00:34:49,629
This is for you.

524
00:34:53,258 --> 00:34:55,093
MISSED CALLS
SU-JONG, SEON

525
00:34:58,305 --> 00:34:59,306
Did you all receive one?

526
00:34:59,389 --> 00:35:00,390
- Yes.
- Yes.

527
00:35:00,473 --> 00:35:04,227
Please raise your voice
as loudly as you can.

528
00:35:04,311 --> 00:35:05,478
- Yes!
- Okay!

529
00:35:05,562 --> 00:35:07,272
Should we practice?

530
00:35:07,355 --> 00:35:08,356
- Okay.
- Okay.

531
00:35:09,316 --> 00:35:13,320
We oppose forced development projects
that rob private property!

532
00:35:13,403 --> 00:35:15,572
- We oppose!
- We oppose!

533
00:35:15,655 --> 00:35:17,616
Suspend all destruction of history!

534
00:35:17,699 --> 00:35:19,618
We shall defend our buildings
with our lives!

535
00:35:19,701 --> 00:35:21,703
- We shall defend!
- We shall defend!

536
00:35:21,995 --> 00:35:23,288
I love the volume today.

537
00:35:24,289 --> 00:35:26,708
- Please keep this up.
- Yes.

538
00:35:26,791 --> 00:35:28,418
- We got this! Let's go!
- Let's go!

539
00:35:28,501 --> 00:35:30,670
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

540
00:35:31,671 --> 00:35:33,381
- Great work today.
- Put it in your pocket.

541
00:35:33,465 --> 00:35:34,924
- Give me a call next time.
- Sure.

542
00:35:35,884 --> 00:35:37,093
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

543
00:35:42,140 --> 00:35:44,059
- You're here.
- Is this where I should film?

544
00:35:44,851 --> 00:35:45,894
You're right on time.

545
00:35:46,311 --> 00:35:48,188
- Make it look good.
- Just keep your promise.

546
