They feel bad?

810
00:54:38,025 --> 00:54:39,359
That's so easy.

811
00:54:39,902 --> 00:54:42,654
You can act like a piece of trash
and just feel bad about it.

812
00:54:44,364 --> 00:54:45,365
Da-rae.

813
00:54:47,242 --> 00:54:48,494
Do you want to live with me?

814
00:54:49,787 --> 00:54:51,997
You already know
what your parents did.

815
00:54:53,040 --> 00:54:54,458
Can you still live with them?

816
00:54:55,083 --> 00:54:56,919
I don't have any family

817
00:54:57,377 --> 00:54:59,046
and you practically don't, either.

818
00:55:00,547 --> 00:55:02,174
So let us be family.

819
00:55:02,716 --> 00:55:04,676
I'll pay for your study abroad.

820
00:55:05,093 --> 00:55:06,094
How about it?

821
00:55:07,095 --> 00:55:08,680
All you need to say is yes.

822
00:55:09,723 --> 00:55:11,099
Just give up on your mom and dad.

823
00:55:16,563 --> 00:55:20,234
(I can't. How can I do that?)

824
00:55:29,409 --> 00:55:34,122
YOU SAID A FAMILIAL RELATIONSHIP
IS ABOUT ACCEPTING LIMITATIONS

825
00:55:37,084 --> 00:55:38,293
I knew you'd say that.

826
00:55:41,338 --> 00:55:43,090
Then you're partially responsible

827
00:55:44,466 --> 00:55:45,968
for things that are about to happen.

828
00:57:27,736 --> 00:57:29,780
SEON

829
00:57:39,414 --> 00:57:40,707
The call cannot be connected.

830
00:57:48,507 --> 00:57:49,508
Hey.

831
00:57:49,716 --> 00:57:50,842
Where are you?

832
00:57:51,385 --> 00:57:53,762
I met with Hwal-sung,
and he didn't know anything.

833
00:57:53,845 --> 00:57:55,138
That's not the problem.

834
00:57:55,222 --> 00:57:58,350
But this punk is always lying,
so I find him hard to believe.

835
00:57:58,934 --> 00:58:00,352
I think Da-rae got kidnapped.

836
00:58:00,435 --> 00:58:01,436
What?

837
00:58:03,313 --> 00:58:04,523
It's Da-rae!

838
00:58:04,940 --> 00:58:07,150
I think Da-rae got kidnapped!

839
00:58:08,318 --> 00:58:09,319
What?

840
00:58:09,403 --> 00:58:10,654
What happened to Da-rae?

841
00:58:11,488 --> 00:58:13,824
I'm going to the police station now

842
00:58:13,907 --> 00:58:15,826
so come quickly, okay?

843
00:59:00,620 --> 00:59:01,621
Da-rae.

844
00:59:04,916 --> 00:59:05,917
Good job.

845
00:59:35,655 --> 00:59:38,575
MAD CONCRETE DREAMS

846
00:59:38,825 --> 00:59:40,077
Was she really abducted?

847
00:59:40,160 --> 00:59:41,870
Yi-gyeong wouldn't do that.

848
00:59:41,953 --> 00:59:43,705
Things can't get any worse.

849
00:59:43,789 --> 00:59:44,873
I've already hit rock bottom.

850
00:59:44,956 --> 00:59:48,376
I just need your mom and dad
to be as broken as I am.

851
00:59:48,460 --> 00:59:49,920
Da-rae knows everything, Su-jong.

852
00:59:50,003 --> 00:59:52,130
Sir, how old is your child?

853
00:59:52,214 --> 00:59:53,215
It hasn't been born yet.

854
00:59:53,548 --> 00:59:55,175
Do you have newborn items?

855
00:59:55,425 --> 00:59:56,426
Who are you?

856
00:59:56,510 --> 00:59:57,719
Why are you doing this to me?

857
00:59:57,803 --> 00:59:59,429
No!

858
00:59:59,513 --> 01:00:01,723
Hwal-sung, I need you to die today.

859
01:00:01,807 --> 01:00:03,892
I fully admit to murdering

860
01:00:03,975 --> 01:00:05,435
Jeon Yi-gyeong's husband,
Min Hwal-sung

861
01:00:05,519 --> 01:00:06,520
and abandoning his body.

862
01:00:19,658 --> 01:00:21,660
Subtitles by Eunsook Youn
and Jennifer Lim
